wordpressPost.title: Backstabbing
wordpressPost.content: Through my recent love of one band The Dresden Dolls I discovered a funny little video they did with Panic! At The Disco, which nicely shows the relationship between mimes and emos … It's a bit strange, but I'm sure deep down they realise they're pretty much the same evil crap.
